  <description><![CDATA[<p>Sestri Levante is one of the most beautiful little towns on the <a data-udi="umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb}" title="Liguria">Ligurian Riviera</a>. It consists of a thin strip of land with a wide beach on one side and the beautiful Bay of Silence on the other and this is linked to a pretty wooded promontory. It is an ancient maritime centre and the old town has cobbled streets and characteristic houses and there is much to see in and around Sestri.</p>]]></description>
