  <insidersGuide><![CDATA[<p style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">Good to know</p>
<ul>
<li>Sestri Levante was an island, but its now linked by a sandbank</li>
<li>It's known as the city of two seas because of its beautiful bays</li>
<li>Take the ferry line 3, 4 or 5 from here to Portovenere and three of the Cinque Terre Villages</li>
</ul>]]></insidersGuide>
